@host = http://localhost:5231

### Health check
GET {{host}}/health

###

### Extract a valid invoice (update path to your actual PNG)
POST {{host}}/api/invoices/extract
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="invoice-valid.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< /Users/cc/BillingExtractor/sample-invoices/invoice-valid.png
--boundary--

###

### Get all saved invoices
GET {{host}}/api/invoices
Accept: application/json

###

### Delete an invoice by ID (replace 1 with the actual ID from GET response)
DELETE {{host}}/api/invoices/1

###
